  <section class="tours">
    <h3 class="title">Guided Tours</h3>
    <p>Our guided tours feature single-day and multiple-day trips with food and water supplied. You just have to bring your pack and be ready for an adventure.</p>
    <hr>
    <ul class="grid">
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/guided1.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="large" style="background-image: url(data/img/guided2.jpg);"></li>
