      <li class="large" style="background-image: url(data/img/guided4.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/guided5.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/mountain2.jpg);"></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="tours">
    <h3 class="title">Photo Tours</h3>
    <p>Our photo tours feature a full day ride on one of our top-tier tour buses through some premier photography landscapes. Don't worry if you don't have a great camera. We have plenty to rent so you can show off your photo skills to your friends.</p>
    <hr>
    <ul class="grid">
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/photo1.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="large" style="background-image: url(data/img/photo2.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="large" style="background-image: url(data/img/photo4.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/photo5.jpg);"></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="tours">
    <h3 class="title">Bicycle Tours</h3>
    <p>Our bicycle tour feature single or multi-day trips through rugged and not-so rugged terrian, it's up to you! We have plenty of trails and rental bikes to choose from. So be prepared for sore legs and plenty of memories.</p>
    <hr>
    <ul class="grid">
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/bike1.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="large" style="background-image: url(data/img/bike2.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="large" style="background-image: url(data/img/bike4.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/bike5.jpg);"></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="tours">
    <h3 class="title">Race Tours</h3>
    <p>Competitive spirit? We have plenty of race options to choose from. Be the first to summit, or reach the hidden gem destination on our mountain trek races.</p>
    <hr>
    <ul class="grid">
      <li class="small" style="background-image: url(data/img/race1.jpg);"></li>
      <li class="large" style="background-image: url(data/img/race2.jpg);"></li>
